Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些上天恩赐的细小水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前起便一直赐予我们情趣与忧愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时很温柔，有时却很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，今宵这场雨会洒在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人和一个女人的过去上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人会被怎样的命运弄湿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没下这场雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人或许会那样想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，今日的对手是neo Turkey的Minaret Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}雨中再会…Falling Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那传闻我听过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期前这国家的GUNDAM突然四处捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伊斯坦堡的西部破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事传遍全世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会成为国家的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武装警察正拼命找他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那完全无用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝会看穿一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相早晚会揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙真迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我已习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我读医学部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他读机械工学部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他是摔跤会的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我读卫星大学时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同级同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我别打扰他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的起动锁匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这种地方重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里是你的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到你也不出奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你还记得这里是我的故乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要快点替你诊治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，给手臂我看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam的细胞！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam和京二·卡休一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡到地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们调查卡休博士的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能找到线索以便\N定下将来对付Devil Gundam的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而根据我们发现的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看见一件可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在注射入老鼠体内的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有问题的Devil Gundam细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称DG细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人震惊的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不只是一种金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它也能和有机物质结合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有生命的细胞一样在体内扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后经过一段潜伏期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤便会开始变成金属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这阶段还能治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但万一脑部被侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就会被Devil Gundam所控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复进行破坏与杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底变成他的木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这方法来增加自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是卡休博士造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam三大理论机能之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我增殖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一我们人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到这种DG细胞的感染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类恐怕会有同一结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一结果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵，莉茵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吓一了跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是一直以来的老毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已经开始康复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之，让我详细检查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹是个医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特，我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以答应我一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你不要告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生有义务为病人保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这阶段还能治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但万一脑部被侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就会重复进行破坏与杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏与杀戮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也不问我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为每一个人都有其苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的雨真不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何时会停雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Falling rain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星里这样称呼预知的下雨天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来，当日也是下雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵？你的名字原来叫莉茵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，爸爸说雨是对大地的恩赐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说我起这名字是要我像雨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为滋润大地的女性，很夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那个下雨天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你便从我面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我很久之后才听到你已经回到neo Japan的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当日，我无论如何一定要见你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们能这样子重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫多蒙的是你男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是工作上的拍档
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞…塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…舍弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？你那么匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真怪呢，根本没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人是Gundam Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙，你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要问他在哪里遇上Devil Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要进行GUNDAM FIGHT也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有病啊，我不会让他那样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你不是我的拍档吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时也是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为医生的不可让病人做出令病情恶化的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为医生…真的只是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你郁郁不欢，让女人跑了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都像笼中鸟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开后我便马上成为Gundam Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在机械工学的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学生时代的摔跤招式给看中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直埋头于战斗与破坏里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此便和你这种善良的人无缘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，某一日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的力量很可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有反抗的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输个一败涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来时，他已经不知所踪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我操纵GUNDAM时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时会好像失去意识一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去意识？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一次，当我醒觉时…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应为祖国尊严而战的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的故乡破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起GUNDAM四处躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来失去知觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来后就见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神的牵引吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候注射镇静剂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道何时又会发作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你出去会马上被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我继续留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许会杀了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是医生啊，我不能舍弃病人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当日本来打算见你决定一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择成为Gundam Fighter平步青云？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是留在研究院和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当日没来是因为讨厌了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来给他们找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料，部队开始集结起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们知道你们窝藏我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你们也会被捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去引开他们的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们趁机逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！塞伊特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！别放过他！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DG细胞开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫我去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了追捕Devil Gundam而参加FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对方是谁也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也喜欢讽刺的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少以GUNDAM FIGHT决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Gundam的自我再生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！他已经是恶魔的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是你认识的塞伊特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特的脑还未被DG细胞感染
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能跟你比赛就是证明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他听到我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就有可能回复清醒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你，听我讲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当日的事，我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Falling rain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预測一样下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打算前去约定的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有点困难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡休世伯他…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙？他回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到爸爸的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要马上回去neo Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非因为讨厌了你，所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特，我求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回我喜欢的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你！塞伊特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开！莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒它只有这机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要杀死塞伊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Devil Gundam有关的人一定要死！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对方是谁也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不留下来可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府知道塞伊特有病后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞伊特也就不会被重判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给这里的医院便行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身为医生的工作结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在再次变回你的拍挡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你，多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想把Devil Gundam的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给这国家罢了

Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:31.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便数千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:35.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:40.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨着 追求着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.91,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:51.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人啊 在我瞳孔的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:56.76,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实摇曳着的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:23:02.07,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何传达才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.55,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让受伤的心与身体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:12.73,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这温暖的怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:18.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在因神秘MS军团而变为废墟的东京
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙和莉茵被一名格斗家救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不正是多蒙的师傅 前代King Of Heart吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动武斗传G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫东方不败！Master Asia出场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


